Package: svgchop
Type: Package
Title: Approximate SVG Elements With Line Segments
Description: Parses SVG elements and approximates them with straight line
  segments.  Only a small set of SVG syntax and commands are recognized.  The
  parsing is done with regex so don't expect it to be robust.  The code is slow
  and hacky.
Version: 0.2.0
